Note: Runa AI Framework - Core Intention Management
Production-grade intention systems for AI agent goal-oriented behavior and intentional stance
Competitive with BDI architectures, SOAR cognitive architecture, and enterprise agent frameworks :End Note

Note: Core intention types for comprehensive goal management
Type called "IntentionType":
    "achievement_intention",
    "maintenance_intention",
    "avoidance_intention",
    "exploratory_intention",
    "reactive_intention",
    "composite_intention",
    "conditional_intention",
    "temporal_intention",
    "collaborative_intention",
    "meta_intention"

Note: Comprehensive intention with full lifecycle management
Type called "Intention":
    "intention_id" as String,
    "intention_type" as IntentionType,
    "goal_specification" as Dictionary,
    "success_criteria" as Dictionary,
    "failure_conditions" as Dictionary,
    "priority_level" as Float,
    "urgency_level" as Float,
    "resource_requirements" as Dictionary,
    "temporal_constraints" as Dictionary,
    "context_dependencies" as Dictionary,
    "preconditions" as List[Dictionary],
    "postconditions" as List[Dictionary],
    "execution_strategy" as Dictionary,
    "monitoring_configuration" as Dictionary,
    "adaptation_rules" as List[Dictionary],
    "intention_metadata" as Dictionary

