Note: Comprehensive intention manager with intelligent coordination
Type called "IntentionManager":
    "manager_id" as String,
    "intention_stacks" as Dictionary,
    "goal_reasoning_engine" as Dictionary,
    "resource_coordinator" as Dictionary,
    "conflict_resolver" as Dictionary,
